<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001552/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The evaluation of the subject will be carried out in a final exam. This final exam is unique, containing a series of exercises that cover the contents taught in the subject.
To pass the subject it is necessary to obtain a minimum score of 5 points out of 10 in the final exam.
Additionally, in this subject progressive evaluation is carried out through exercises in class throughout the course. Progressive evaluation tests allow up to an additional 20% to be added to the grade,
provided that a minimum of 4 points is obtained in the final exam.
The progressive evaluation is not liberating from facing the final exam.
In case of failing the final exam, the progressive evaluation grade will be saved until the next examination call.
Practical labs are compulsory to pass the subject."""@es ;
